Package: astro
Type: Package
Title: Astronomy Functions, Tools and Routines for R
Version: 2.0
Date: 2019-01-26
Author: Lee Kelvin <l.s.kelvin@ljmu.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Lee Kelvin <l.s.kelvin@ljmu.ac.uk>
Description: A series of functions, tools and routines for everyday use within astronomy, e.g.: cosmology; FITS file manipulation; the Sersic function; plotting; data handling/manipulation; statistics; general convenience functions and scripting tools.
License: GPL (>= 3)
